{"tid":1834330,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【回帶】陳肇始拒絕呼籲公眾出席公眾場合時佩戴口罩保護自己","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T23:25:53.000Z","uid":15696,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ed8720212658b276ebb2f93dd89d1d3f80900c","tid":1834330,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:37:14.000Z","msg":"忌諱蒙面法 陳肇始拒籲戴罩<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本周五法庭將就蒙面法上訴裁決，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始昨日僅呼籲市民洗手，卻未有提醒市民戴口罩預防武漢肺炎，被問及會否呼籲公眾出席公眾場合時佩戴口罩保護自己，陳肇始拒絕回答，僅重申蒙面法與任何公共衞生措施沒有牴觸，「如果病人有需要戴口罩嘅時候，係冇牴觸，醫護人員如果有需要去做佢嘅工作嘅時候，如果有需要佩戴口罩係冇牴觸嘅」。<br />\n黃國桐：有防疫需要<br />\n<br />\n蒙面法列明，「因先前已存在的醫學或健康理由」而在集結或遊行中使用蒙面物，仍屬免責辯護範圍內。律師黃國桐認為，即使蒙面法生效，在目前衞生情況和健康風險下，在公眾場合有預防疾病需要，警方亦不可以此法例拘捕蒙面示威者。<br />\n<br />\n立法會衞生事務委員會成員黃碧雲批評，預防疾病是否屬於「醫學或健康理由」並不清晰，蒙面法對防疫有害無益，凸顯了法例漏洞，法例亦只為削弱港人表達和集會自由，應予廢絕。她又批評陳肇始不肯呼籲公眾戴口罩防疫，有所失職，「面對防疫問題，你仲左閃右避，政治立場行先」。她建議公眾自行決定是否戴口罩，「唔使旨意政府保護市民健康」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20200108/20839696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F20839696&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=7995f6dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F20839696&h=b59b7764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20200108/20839696</a>"},{"pid":"f1b4c8c14f69cded6c771f17edbbdaa82e1f1e1d","tid":1834330,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ebd13dc924ce7202607cf258c9314796008a924","tid":1834330,"uid":15696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"市民得到訊息就係政府唔畀戴口罩"},{"pid":"f858c0910d57bd8cdf3520a4cb55ef82e9b70644","tid":1834330,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"「如果病人有需要戴口罩嘅時候，係冇牴觸，醫護人員如果有需要去做佢嘅工作嘅時候，如果有需要佩戴口罩係冇牴觸嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府: 冇病都係唔畀戴口罩</span>"},{"pid":"f03ab88f8d0c2b146d729d57ec0b44522a07cdee","tid":1834330,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"好人好姐帶咩口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家一出街見到藍屍我即刻扯鳩佢口罩"},{"pid":"6846f8f66faa5158c005b5422cc334201fc022f7","tid":1834330,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"依家一出街見到藍屍即刻扯鳩佢口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0imDbBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0imDbBy.jpg&h=310b5226&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a7903ed8b00f30a776c9c318cf9ec857a53240f","tid":1834330,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd656e6234298b6497ee94363263f6ca8b62dbee","tid":1834330,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"同得777做fd你覺得佢係好人？"},{"pid":"47e67be71202daabd61c480f9ee7b5968878422c","tid":1834330,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"成班狗官等運到<br />\n好啦又係百年一遇病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d752587821c12c51cca7955792a4b9c89a6cf1d1","tid":1834330,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/z6wLAWi.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"52c23639aed9bb1422c73923a046919ba5de5789","tid":1834330,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢肺炎 香港封關</spa